column5: Have to pick my daughter up off a bus at 9:15pm... in Scarberia.
I was at the one in Cincy last Friday, didn't want to fight the weekend crowd so I went at lunch time. Expensive lunch break
.....the  nerve of you. Has lLeah seen that pic. I know you've got the plastic hidden somewhere Wayne.
